codex
I have enough context to rewrite the verifier around the real vulnerable path: a V2-style router spending the nominal `_amountIn` via `transferFrom`, funded by a Uniswap/Sushi flashswap rather than Aave. I’m replacing the generic router-wrapper guesses with direct router payloads, broader fee-token discovery, and same-tx deterministic flashswap repayment.
